title: The World's OLDEST Human | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 29
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!


THE BABES talk GETTING OLD! Chris has the sniffles this episode and the babes hop right into how tissues are made and how many are used each year. How many tissue brands are there? The babes watch a viral video of a teenager attacking a bear in her backyard. Could you survive a bear attack? How do you deal with a bear when confronted?! Sal has an INSANE story about bears from Impractical Jokers. What are the most dangerous animals? One national park has the most dangerous bears! Sal talks about the time he got attacked by a CLOUDED LEOPARD while at a zoo. Hippos are a weird animal...WHY ARE THEY SO THICCCC. Shout out sploofs! What would you do if you found out a person you fell in love with was a terrorist? What's the oldest person you could have intercourse with? Shout out the OLDEST human on Earth Kane Tanaka! She is now our BIGGEST HERO ON THE PLANET! GOD BLESS HER! Imagine being alive for 120 years? The babes get a NEW painting from a TALENTED FAN! How to get really old....HEY BABE!
